---------------------------------
VisIt Plugin for NIMROD HDF5 Data
---------------------------------

This plugin reads NIMROD HDF5 as described in nimrod.pdf. The plugin will 
handle only three-dimensional structured meshes in Cartesian coordinates.

This plugin requires that VisIt is compiled with HDF5 support.

